{"tid":2358362,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李顯龍接種首劑輝瑞疫苗證安全有效 習近平表示... ...","createTime":"2021-01-08T05:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T05:48:23.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"28af94fbde6c85531d5e5a642aa506f3c966e495","tid":2358362,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:33:55.000Z","msg":"李顯龍接種首劑輝瑞疫苗　冀向國民展示信心 <br />\n<br />\n新加坡今日起為公共醫療機構的醫護人員接種新型冠狀病毒疫苗，總理李顯龍亦到醫院，接種首劑疫苗，說要向國民展示政府對疫苗的安全及效力有信心。李顯龍在社交網站上載接種疫苗的短片，醫護人員在幫他注射後，請他到休息室等候。李顯龍表示，他在休息室接受半小時的觀察，以防出現過敏反應等副作用，最終並無不適。 <br />\n<br />\n新加坡目前只是批准使用輝瑞與BioNTech合作研製的疫苗，下月開始會為長者免費接種。當局亦已預先採購莫德納及科興疫苗，局期望在今年第三季買到足夠劑量，讓全國570萬人接種。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2373935\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2373935&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIfrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=1b577131\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2373935</a>"},{"pid":"086b65d2bc3fd4b13205a1f1c695d1d65fc3bee1","tid":2358362,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:48:23.000Z","msg":"習近平表示打呢隻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2825000/2829781/20201216_BIONTECH_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2825000%2F2829781%2F20201216_BIONTECH_1024.jpg&h=86154386&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}